---
# HOW TO USE GIT FOR THE DELETION OF A CERTAIN FILE
---

```
git pull origin master   # pull project from remote repository
dir   # view files/dirs
git rm -r --cached _filenameORdirname_   # delete a file or dir
git commit -m 'description'   # commit with description
git push -u origin master   # push this update to github
```

## Preparation:
  1. Download Git Bash
  2. Open Git Bash and **cd** to target path
